    "contents": {
      "kind": "markdown",
      "value": "### Slate component Card\n\n```slate\nimport Card from \"./Card.slate\"\n```\n\nImports a `.slate` component. Use it as a template element and pass props with attributes.\n\nExample:\n```slate\n<Card title=\"Hello\">\n  <p>Content</p>\n</Card>\n```\n\n---\n\n```ts\n(alias) const Card: Component<Props, __SlateInferredSlots>\nimport Card\n```"
    }
  },
  "hoverRune": {
    "range": {
      "start": {
        "line": 4,
        "character": 16
      },
      "end": {
        "line": 4,
        "character": 21
      }
    },
    "contents": {
      "kind": "markdown",
      "value": "```ts\nfunction $prop<\"primary\">(name: string, defaultValue?: \"primary\" | undefined): \"primary\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### $prop\n\n```slate\n$prop<T>(name: string, defaultValue?: T): T\n```\n\nDeclares a single component prop and returns the provided value or the default value.\n\nExample:\n```slate\nconst title = $prop(\"title\", \"Untitled\");\n```"
    }
  },
  "hoverEach": {
    "range": {
      "start": {
        "line": 15,
        "character": 1
      },
      "end": {
        "line": 15,
        "character": 6
      }
    },
    "contents": {
      "kind": "markdown",
      "value": "### {#each ...}\n\n```slate\n{#each items as item, index} ... {/each}\n```\n\nIterates over an iterable or array-like value and renders the block for each item.\n\nExample:\n```slate\n{#each items as item, index}\n  <li>{index}: {item}</li>\n{/each}\n```"
    }
  },
  "hoverSlotDirective": {
    "range": {
      "start": {
        "line": 9,
        "character": 10
      },
      "end": {
        "line": 9,
        "character": 18
      }
    },
    "contents": {
      "kind": "markdown",
      "value": "```ts\n(property) \"header\"?: ((data: {\n    title: \"Hello\";\n    tail: 1;\n}) => unknown) | undefined\n```\n\n---\n\n### slot:*\n\n```slate\n<header slot:header={{ title, icon }}>...</header>\n```\n\nProvides content for a named slot on a child component. The directive name after `slot:` selects the outlet.\n\nExample:\n```slate\n<Card>\n  <header slot:header={{ title, icon }}>{title}</header>\n</Card>\n```"
    }
  },
